stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> pending: mint (not yet settled)
    pending --> settled: payment settles
    settled --> active: well-formed VIR counts toward reputation
    settled --> refunded: refund (by agreement)
    refunded --> valid_evidence: NOT invalidated; engine interprets
    settled --> charged_back: chargeback (dispute)
    settled --> disputed: dispute opened
    active --> charged_back: later reversal
    charged_back --> invalidated: Settlement-Consistency
    disputed --> invalidated: Settlement-Consistency
    invalidated --> [*]
